Get detailed documentation for Ant Design specific components
Applicable scenarios:
1. The user asks how to use specific components;
2. The user needs to view the api properties of the component;

If not supported, add it as a workspace dependency to the package.json file.

List update logs for Ant Design specific components

Applicable scenarios:
1. The user asks for the update log of a specific component;
2. When users need to implement relevant functions, they help determine which version they will be implemented in, and decide whether they need to upgrade dependencies;
